Package: fnd-client
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python3:Depends}, python3, python3-yaml, python3-cryptography, python3-pynacl
Description: Friendly Network Detection client service
 A daemon that determines the current trusted network by verifying a
 cryptographic challenge-response with configured FND servers and exposes
 the resulting network id via a protected UNIX socket for other local
 applications.
